    <div class="body">
        <p>In Zend_Http_Client incubator version, the _write() method is written,</p>

<pre><code>    fwrite($socket, $request . "\r\n");
</code></pre>

<p>But, is CRLF needed here?</p>

<p>$request set $headers + "\r\n" + $body in Zend_Http_Client_Abstract::request() method,
so I think it will be</p>

<pre><code>    fwrite($socket, $request);
</code></pre>

<p>Please check it.</p>

